properties.Name: Sodic East
properties.Description: Sodic East is a modern residential compound located in New Cairo. It offers a range of luxurious villas and apartments surrounded by lush green landscapes. Residents can enjoy amenities such as swimming pools, sports facilities, parks, and a vibrant community atmosphere.

properties.Name: Sarai
properties.Description: Sarai is a well-planned residential community situated in New Cairo. It boasts a contemporary design and a wide variety of residential units, including apartments, townhouses, and villas. Sarai features beautiful parks, lakes, retail outlets, and recreational facilities, providing a comfortable and convenient lifestyle for its residents.

properties.Name: El Patio Prime
properties.Description: El Patio Prime is a prestigious residential compound located in the heart of New Cairo. It offers high-end villas and apartments designed with elegance and modernity in mind. The compound features landscaped gardens, walking trails, a clubhouse, and a range of amenities, providing a serene and luxurious living experience.

properties.Name: Maadi View
properties.Description: Maadi View is a residential compound situated in the desirable neighborhood of Maadi, in the southern part of Cairo. It offers a mix of apartment buildings and villas with stunning views of the surrounding greenery. Maadi View provides a tranquil environment, proximity to amenities, and a strong sense of community.

properties.Name: Madinaty
properties.Description: Madinaty is a large-scale residential development located in New Cairo. It offers a comprehensive range of housing options, including apartments, townhouses, and villas. With its well-planned infrastructure, parks, schools, commercial areas, and recreational facilities, Madinaty aims to provide a self-sufficient and family-friendly community.

properties.Name: El Shorouk Springs
properties.Description: El Shorouk Springs is a residential compound located in El Shorouk City, near New Cairo. It offers a mix of villas and apartments surrounded by landscaped gardens and water features. The compound provides a peaceful environment, recreational spaces, and various amenities for residents to enjoy.

properties.Name: O West
properties.Description: O West is an upscale residential compound located in the Sheikh Zayed area. It offers a modern and luxurious living experience with a range of residential units, including villas, townhouses, and apartments. O West features beautifully landscaped gardens, recreational facilities, shopping malls, and a community center, providing residents with a comfortable and convenient lifestyle.

properties.Name: The Crown
properties.Description: The Crown is an exclusive residential compound situated in New Cairo. It prides itself on offering lavish villas and apartments designed with sophistication and elegance. The Crown provides a gated community environment with lush green spaces, sports facilities, clubhouse amenities, and a tranquil atmosphere that caters to residents seeking a refined and upscale lifestyle.

properties.Name: Al Rabwa
properties.Description: Nestled in the prestigious area of Sheikh Zayed, Al Rabwa is an exclusive residential compound that offers a luxurious and refined living experience. This sought-after community showcases a collection of elegant villas and residences, meticulously designed to provide residents with the utmost comfort and sophistication.

properties.Name: Mountain View October Park
properties.Description: Mountain View is a renowned residential compound that has several projects in different areas of Cairo, including New Cairo and Sheikh Zayed. It offers a variety of housing options, such as villas, townhouses, and apartments, designed to accommodate different preferences and needs. Mountain View developments often feature landscaped gardens, scenic views, recreational facilities, and a strong emphasis on community living.

properties.Name: Keeva
properties.Description: Keeva is a residential compound located in New Cairo, offering a blend of modern architecture and serene surroundings. It presents a mix of contemporary villas and apartments, complemented by lush green landscapes, walking paths, and recreational areas. Keeva aims to provide a harmonious living environment for residents seeking comfort and tranquility.

properties.Name: New Giza
properties.Description: New Giza is a prestigious residential and golf community situated in the Giza Governorate, near Cairo. It features luxurious villas and apartments designed to offer a high standard of living. New Giza boasts beautifully landscaped gardens, a championship golf course, sports facilities, restaurants, and a vibrant community atmosphere, providing residents with an exclusive and upscale lifestyle.

properties.Name: Royal City
properties.Description: Royal City is a residential compound located in New Cairo, offering a mix of elegant villas and apartments. It focuses on providing a family-friendly environment with spacious homes, landscaped gardens, children's playgrounds, and recreational amenities. Royal City aims to create a sense of community and a comfortable living experience for its residents.

properties.Name: Allegeria
properties.Description: Allegria is an upscale residential compound situated in the Sheikh Zayed area. It offers a range of luxurious villas and apartments surrounded by lush green landscapes and stunning views. Allegria features a golf course, clubhouse, sports facilities, and a variety of amenities, providing residents with an exclusive and refined living environment.

properties.Name: Beverly Hills
properties.Description: Beverly Hills is a residential compound located in Sheikh Zayed, offering a mix of upscale villas and apartments. It is known for its distinctive architecture, well-maintained landscaping, and a range of amenities such as swimming pools, sports facilities, and recreational spaces. Beverly Hills aims to provide a luxurious and comfortable living experience for its residents.

properties.Name: Cleopatra Square
properties.Description: Cleopatra Square is a residential compound situated in New Cairo, inspired by ancient Egyptian architectural themes. It offers a variety of residential units, including apartments and villas, designed to blend modern living with a touch of history. Cleopatra Square features landscaped gardens, water features, communal areas, and a range of amenities, providing residents with a unique and captivating living environment.
